  "/ghost-shower-2020-21": {
    title: "Ghost Shower (2020-21) | He Jin Jang Dance",
    html: "<div class=\"content-page works-detail-page\">\n  <h1 style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Ghost Shower (2020-21)</h1>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Ghost Shower is a co-created transdisciplinary work involving 4 choreographers and 1 film artist. This GPS-based application allows users to record memories of &lsquo;not being able to take care of someone,' and these voices travel the world as ghosts with algorithmic choreography. Users can place their voices anywhere in the world using this app, and when other users approach the area, they can listen to the voices of the released memories. They can also watch how the voices move and \"dance\" like weather patterns on the map via the application.\n​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Created and Produced by Sleungst and Friends (He Jin Jang, Bittnarie Shin, Min Kyung Lee, Seyoung Jeong, Su-Mi Jang)\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    App Advising by Boram Kim\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Illustration by Minha Yoo\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Sound Design by R&eacute;mi Klemensiewicz\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Project Manager by Nayoung Kim\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    App Development by Laidback\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Supported by: Seoul Foundation for Arts and Culture, Seoul Metropolitan City\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n    Link to App\n  </p>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <img src=\"/images/073f40_8ccb53e25cfd4bdcb82fe37ee7f8880e_mv2.png\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" alt=\"Ghost Shower (2020-21)\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <img src=\"/images/073f40_681ce271fdf540d69ac54bcf9894d1cc_mv2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" alt=\"Ghost Shower (2020-21)\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <img src=\"/images/073f40_ffaa9df8d21b4c32b39015d41dbc52c3_mv2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" alt=\"Ghost Shower (2020-21)\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <img src=\"/images/073f40_dd84b7763db246169ad373fef9f8e764_mv2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" alt=\"Ghost Shower (2020-21)\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <img src=\"/images/073f40_7302fd679c0644038d479d138cf2ec24_mv2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" alt=\"Ghost Shower (2020-21)\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </div>\n\n  <button class=\"accordion-toggle\" style=\"background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a; width: 100%; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    한국어 보기 +\n  </button>\n  <div class=\"accordion-content\" style=\"display: none; padding: 20px 0;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      슬릉쓰트와 친구들 콜렉티브 공동기획 GPS 기반 앱 창작.&lsquo;누군가를 돌보지 못한 기억'을 녹음하고 앱의 지도 위에 놓아주면, 그 목소리는 알고리듬 안무에 의해 세계를 유령처럼 여행한다. 세계 어디에서나 위치 반경 안에 들어가면 그 목소리를 들을 수 있으며, 팬데믹 시대의 돌봄 행위가 안무된다. 팬데믹 시대에 우리는 어떤 방식으로 만날 수 있을까? 둘 이상의 영혼이 만날 때 일어나야 하는 일은 결국 돌봄아닐까? 예술과 테라피, 게임이 만난 어플에서 접속자는 각자 속에 숨어지낸 유령을 만난다.\n \n    </p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      공동기획 및 제작. 슬릉쓰트와 친구들 (신빛나리, 이민경, 장수미, 장혜진, 정세영)\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      앱 연출 자문. 김보람\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      일러스트레이션. 유민하\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      사운드 디자인. 해미 클레멘세비츠\n    </p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n      후원. 서울문화재단, 서울특별시\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },

