    title: 'Art Scene, January lssue, I bet you’d put that on, 2023, Mingwan Kim (Critic) /『아트신』 1월호, <당신이 그런 것을 입게 될 줄 알았어>, 2023년, 김민관 평론가 | He Jin Jang Dance',
